Author: supreme888
Title: [ANN][Pre-ICO] MoBee - WORLDWIDE VIRTUAL MOBILE OPERATOR
Body: Hello  MoBee is an ecosystem. The MBE token is an internal payment medium of the MoBee ecosystem and is intended for all types of operations. This makes it a key factor of the MoBee economy. The MBE token will circulate in the environment in transactions between the participants of the NetWorx platform ( freelancers professional, contractors, mobile operators) and virtual mobile operator MoBee, subscribers, partner networks Due to this, it will be possible to provide services to subscribers at low prices, as well as financial services and the ability to make purchases. Detailed info you can see here https://mobeetel.co/storage/moBee_en.pdf
